## 🚀 Phase Highlights

### Phase 4: Autonomous Harvester
- Implemented [kaggle_automated_harvester.py](file:///home/kizabgd/Desktop/Istrazivanje/scripts/kaggle_automated_harvester.py) for recursive SOTA discovery.
- Automated API credential recovery for 401 errors.

### Phase 5: Memory Optimization
- Added **Model Lineage** tracking to prevent "cloning" of weak strategies.
- Implemented **Atomic Commit** logic for the SQL Knowledge Base.

### Phase 6: Security & Compliance
- **KeyVault**: Centralized API key management with rotation support.
- **AuditLogger**: Detailed logging of all external AI calls for cost and performance tracking.
- **Rate Limits**: [JudgeGuard](file:///home/kizabgd/Desktop/Istrazivanje/scripts/judge_guard.py#82-465) now enforces daily budgets to avoid API locks.

### Phase 7: Monitoring & Testing
- **Dashboard API**: Serves real-time throughput and latency KPIs.
- **Unit Tests**: Full suite coverage for Discovery and Memory cores.

